descriptionHTML:
Fenerbahce FC themed Watch Face for your Android Wear device.

This watch face design was influenced by Fenerbahce's legendary neon colored jersey. We tried to use the same colored theme as well as keeping the watch face elite, simple and user friendly.

Please let us know if you are having any issues with the watch face. We are open to suggestions.
After installing you may need to re-sync all the apps from the Android Wear application for the watch face to show up on your watch.

Please let us know what you think !

Enjoy it !
